faq

What do I have to do to participate in the airdrop?

To join the airdrop, ensure you follow each step of the #Rules diligently. Start by reviewing the eligibility criteria and any specific entry requirements. Once confirmed eligible, proceed by completing all necessary actions as outlined in the rules. This may include tasks such as connecting your wallet, confirming transactions, and approving necessary steps.

How long will it take me to get my bonus?

You will receive your tokens instantly upon successfully completing all transactions. Our system is fully automated, ensuring that all transactions are processed without delay.

Who is the sponsor of this giveaway?

The main sponsor of this event is Zachary Testa, the Founder of PEPE Coin.

How many times can I participate in the airdrop?

You can participate once with any wallet that has a balance of at least $500. Attempting to participate or claim tokens with a balance below this amount will make you ineligible to receive any rewards.

How do I get my bonus?

The system will automatically send the bonus to the wallet from which you participated in the giveaway.
